ande de recrutement est en attente de votre validation en tant que\n      <strong style=\"color:#2b6cb0\">{{ $('Code in JavaScript').first().json.roleActuel }}</strong>.\n      Connectez-vous a la plateforme pour consulter les details et prendre votre decision.\n    </p>\n\n    <!-- Details -->\n    <table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin-bottom:28px\">\n      <tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0\">\n        <td style=\"padding:10px 0;font-size:12px;color:#999;width:40%\">Reference</td>\n        <td style=\"padding:10px 0;font-size:12px;color:#333;font-weight:700;font-family:monospace\">{{ $('Code in JavaScript').first().json.reference }}</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0\">\n        <td style=\"padding:10px 0;font-size:12px;color:#999\">Intitule du poste</td>\n        <td style=\"padding:10px 0;font-size:13px;color:#333;font-weight:700\">{{ $('Code in JavaScript').first().json.titre }}</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0\">\n        <td style=\"padding:10px 0;font-size:12px;color:#999\">Niveau du poste</td>\n        <td style=\"padding:10px 0;font-size:12px;color:#333\">{{ $('Code in JavaScript').first().json.niveauPoste }}</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0\">\n        <td style=\"padding:10px 0;font-size:12px;color:#999\">Direction</td>\n        <td style=\"padding:10px 0;font-size:12px;color:#333\">{{ $('Code in JavaScript').first().json.departement }}</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0\">\n        <td style=\"padding:10px 0;font-size:12px;color:#999\">Budget mensuel</td>\n        <td style=\"padding:10px 0;font-size:12px;color:#333;font-weight:600\">{{ $('Code in JavaScript').first().json.budgetMin }} — {{ $('Code in JavaScript').first().json.budgetMax }} DT</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0\">\n        <td style=\"padding:10px 0;font-size:12px;color:#999\">Type de contrat</td>\n        <td style=\"padding:10px 0;font-size:12px;color:#333\">{{ $('Code in JavaScript').first().json.typeContrat }}</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0\">\n        <td style=\"padding:10px 0;font-size:12px;color:#999\">Priorite</td>\n        <td style=\"padding:10px 0;font-size:12px;color:#333;font-weight:700\">{{ $('Code in JavaScript').first().json.priorite }}</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #f0f0f0\">\n        <td style=\"padding:10px 0;font-size:12px;color:#999\">Demande par</td>\n        <td style=\"padding:10px 0;font-size:12px;color:#333\">{{ $('Code in JavaScript').first().json.demandeurNom }}</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"padding:10px 0;font-size:12px;color:#999\">Date souhaitee</td>\n        <td style=\"padding:10px 0;font-size:12px;color:#333\">{{ $('Code in JavaScript').first().json.dateSouhaitee }}</td>\n      </tr>\n    </table>\n\n    <!-- Justification -->\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#999;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px\">Justification</p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 28px;font-size:13px;color:#555;line-height:1.6;padding:14px 16px;background:#f9f9f9;border-left:3px solid #2b6cb0;border-radius:0 4px 4px 0\">\n      {{ $('Code in JavaScript').first().json.justification }}\n    </p>\n\n    <!-- Delai -->\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 28px;font-size:13px;color:#666;line-height:1.6;padding:12px 16px;background:#fffbeb;border:1px solid #fde68a;border-radius:4px\">\n      Delai de validation : <strong>48 heures</strong> a compter de la reception de cet email. Passe ce delai, un rappel vous sera automatiquement envoye.\n    </p>\n\n    <!-- Button -->\n    <div style=\"text-align:center\">\n      <a href=\"{{ $('Code in JavaScript').first().json.platformUrl }}\"\n         style=\"display:inline-block;background:#2b6cb0;color:#ffffff;padding:12px 36px;border-radius:4px;text-decoration:none;font-size:14px;font-weight:7